data.description: Need more space? Well....we have it here in this well landscaped, beautiful updated brick basement rancher in wonderful Shaconage. 3 BR/3 BA with a sunroom on each level overlooking the open field in the back, you can relax and watch the birds and other wildlife. 4 car garage for your cars and other toys. Wood flooring in living room, kitchen and dining room. Split bedroom design with a beautiful & bright living room with gas fireplace. To the right are two good sized bedrooms and a full bath in the hall. To the left is the dining area with sliders to the sun room and the large kitchen and pantry. Then you can enter the large laundry room with sink and shelving. Off to the right you enter the main bedroom ensuite with dual sinks, jetted tub, and walk-in shower. There are also his & her walk in closets. Down in the basement is a full bath and a huge recreation/family room area with sliders out to the sunroom. There is a separate craft room and off of that a safe room for storm & storage. All of the windows have been updated with Andersen windows which will save you money. Back yard has raised beds for gardening, good size grassy area for kids and of course, concrete for those basketball games. The front of the home has lush grass and is beautifully landscaped. You currently will have the option of selecting flooring for the bedrooms. Owners had planned on changing flooring out and pulled up the carpet but then the move came so you have a clean slate for whatever you like. This home flows well and has access to back yard from both levels. Just a warm family home in a friendly great neighborhood.
